@page "/analytics-demo"

<PageTitle>Analytics Demo</PageTitle>

<h1>Analytics Components Demo</h1>

<p>This page demonstrates the analytics integration provided by Osirion.Blazor.</p>

<div class="alert alert-success">
    <h4 class="alert-heading">Active Analytics:</h4>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Microsoft Clarity</strong>: Active (demo-clarity-id)</li>
        <li><strong>Matomo Analytics</strong>: Disabled for demo</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<p>The analytics components are loaded automatically via <code>App.razor</code> and work across all render modes.</p>

<h2>Features</h2>
<ul>
    <li>SSR compatible - no JavaScript required</li>
    <li>Configuration via dependency injection</li>
    <li>Automatic page view tracking</li>
    <li>Works with both static and interactive pages</li>
</ul>

<div class="mt-4">
    <h3>Configuration Example</h3>
    <pre><code class="language-csharp">
builder.Services.AddOsirion(osirion => {
    osirion.UseAnalytics(analytics => {
        analytics.AddClarity(options => {
            options.SiteId = "your-clarity-id";
            options.Enabled = true;
        });
        analytics.AddMatomo(options => {
            options.SiteId = "your-matomo-id";
            options.TrackerUrl = "https://your-matomo-url/";
            options.Enabled = true;
        });
    });
});
    </code></pre>
</div>